      "writtenOn": "2019-02-21T21:24:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In your design doc, there will be renderers other than DefaultFrameRenderer, videoRenderer for instance. \n\nCould you have an abstract class for all of them, something like PlaybackCameraRenderer?\n\nAlso I think the *impl class should not be declared/defined in the header file, in which you expose the *impl to public (anti-pattern). One solution maybe move DefaultFrameRenderer here from camera-videoplayback.cpp\n\nAs in your design, in the next steps, you may use multiplexer as factory, since it knows everything.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 32,
        "startChar": 6,
        "endLine": 32,
        "endChar": 30
      },
      "revId": "680583e6fb625ca3368efdd5ff06e952febdbebc",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "d585697c_1dd7773e",
