        "id": 1414904
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-02-22T01:29:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think the virtualscene::CameraRenderer is a sufficient abstract class for all of them for now. I don\u0027t expect them to have any extra features.\n\nI properly set up a PIMPL pattern for now, but I agree the multiplexer will likely use a factory in the future.",
